{"data":{"metadata":{"authors":{},"created_at":1641172542000,"identifier":"/docs/globals/contents","modified_at":1641172542000,"sections":[{"identifier":"contents","level":1,"text":"Contents"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"contents-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {Box} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Box palette=\"accent\" contents={[\"mobile\", \"tablet\"]}>\n    I have no styling on Mobile / Tablet Viewports.\n</Box>\n\n<Box\n    palette=\"affirmative\"\n    contents={[\"desktop\", \"widescreen\"]}\n>\n    I have no styling on Desktop / Widescreen\n    Viewports.\n</Box>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Contents Preview"}],"title":"Contents"},"references":{"custom_properties":{},"events":{},"properties":{"*":[{"name":"contents","description":"Alters the Component to removes bounding box / stylings from the Component, acting as a blank container for child content.","types":["boolean","{VIEWPORT}"]}]},"slots":{}},"render":"<h1 id=\"contents\">Contents</h1>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: New since <code>v0.5.0</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>All Components have access to the <code>data-contents</code> global HTML attribute via the <code>contents</code> property which <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/display#box\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">removes the Component's bounding box / stylings</a> from the DOM tree.</p>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: The REPL currently does not support viewport values. Resize your Browser instead.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: By passing an array, you can set <a href=\"../framework/responsitivity\" svelte:prefetch=\"true\">responsive values</a>. e.g. <code>contents={[&quot;mobile&quot;, &quot;tablet&quot;]}</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"contents-preview\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span c